org.apache.juneau.svl

Class VarResolverContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.juneau.Context
      • org.apache.juneau.svl.VarResolverContext

  • public class VarResolverContext
extends Context
    Configurable properties on the VarResolver class.

    Used to associate Vars and context objects with VarResolvers.

    See ContextFactory for more information about context properties.

    See Also:
    org.apache.juneau.svl

    • Field Detail

      • SVL_vars

        public static final String SVL_vars
        An explicit list of Java classes to be excluded from consideration as being beans (Set<Class>).

        Not-bean classes are typically converted to Strings during serialization even if they appear to be bean-like.
